&lt;div class="section" id="clean-chapters"&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Clean Chapters&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;pre class="code ipython"&gt;&lt;a name="rest_code_012b120504a84860b3b01e6915e3e99c-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="kn"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nn"&gt;re&lt;/span&gt;
